2nd May 1923 - 26th November 2014
Your life was a blessing your memory treasured every day
An amazing Mum, Nan & Great Grandma
Peter Paul Zammit
7th May 1922 - 10th May 2012
A wonderful dad, grandad & great grandad. In memory of all
the happy times spent here in this park with your grandchildren"┐
